Transmutation
Level: Druid 2
Components : V,S
Casting Time: 1 Action
Range: Close
Target: One Creature
Duration: Instant
Save: No
SR: Yes
Meta Magic: Still, Silent, Quicken

<i>Whipping your head forward with the last word of the spell, you spit a globule of dark liquid at your foe.</i>

You spit caustic saliva into your target's eyes with a successful ranged touch attack. A -4 Penalty applies to the attack roll. The subject is blinded until it can seek treatment.

